~ SpikeTutorial
Now that the ball has gone up, you have to spike it!
You are currently in control of the Spiker.
Use the A and D keys to move around.
Move yourself underneath the ball, then press the W key to jump.
Then, once the spiker is right below the ball, press W again to spike.
Don't worry if you get it wrong the first time; you'll be able to try again!
do end_dialogue()